        {
            "title": "中國建材料首季虧損收益至5.2億元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國建材(03323)公布，預期今年首季權益持有人應佔虧損5.2億元(人民幣．下同)，虧損按年收窄61.48%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，季度虧損收窄，主要因為主要產品水泥、玻璃纖維的銷售價格上升和銷售成本下降，以及風電葉片、塗料的銷量增加所致，但部分被水泥的銷量下降所抵銷。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14859635-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%bb%ba%e6%9d%90%e6%96%99%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e6%94%b6%e7%9b%8a%e8%87%b35-2%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/03323.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 16:40:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英國3月通脹率放緩至2.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國3月通脹按年升2.6%，較2月放緩0.2個百分點，略低於市場預期。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英倫銀行預計，今年第3季通脹率會升至3.7%的高位，接近央行目標的1倍，主要受能源成本、公用事業、車費等影響。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場較早時預期，央行下月會議減息0.25厘。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14859552-%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b3%e6%9c%88%e9%80%9a%e8%84%b9%e7%8e%87%e6%94%be%e7%b7%a9%e8%87%b32-6-2",
